ComicInfo.Summary:
The lovely ladies of Street Fighter take a break from fist fights and tournaments to hit up the world's hottest beaches, pools and volleyball courts! Everyone from Chun-li to Laura to Juri shows off their favorite swimwear in this one-shot pin-up special!
